<taxonomicName box="[1034,1167,1943,1966]" class="Insecta" family="Miridae" genus="Pherolepis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longipilus">
<emphasis box="[1034,1167,1943,1966]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">P. longipilus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(male): 37. Lateral view of head; 38. Scent-gland evaporatory area; 39. Simple setae on scutellum; 40. Simple setae on hemelytron. 41–42. Parempodia.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/191195/files/figure.png" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" targetBox="[236,1424,218,891]" targetPageId="13">
<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1436,928,986]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,348,928,952]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">FIGURES 43–48.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName box="[355,582,928,951]" class="Insecta" family="Miridae" genus="Pherolepis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longipilus" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[355,582,928,951]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">
Pherolepis 
<taxonomicName box="[475,582,928,951]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" rank="species" species="longipilus" status="sp. nov.">longipilus</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
